        %br
        出品・購入回数も業界最多です！
        %br
        ほしかったあの商品に出会えるかもしれません。
  .top-page-main__features
    .top-page-main__features__head
      FURIMAの特徴
    .top-page-main__features__items
      .top-page-main__features__items__1
        .top-page-main__features__items__1__img
          = image_tag "icon-01.png", width: "70%"
        .top-page-main__features__items__1__subtitle
          簡単に売り買いできる
        .top-page-main__features__items__1__detail
          スマホひとつで、いつでもどこでも簡単に出品・購入が可能！
      .top-page-main__features__items__2
        .top-page-main__features__items__2__img
          = image_tag "icon-03.png", width: "70%"
        .top-page-main__features__items__2__subtitle
          売上金は即日振込みに対応
        .top-page-main__features__items__2__detail
          午前9時までに振込を依頼いただければ、翌日に指定の口座に入金いたします!
      .top-page-main__features__items__3
        .top-page-main__features__items__3__img
          = image_tag "icon-04.png", width: "70%"
        .top-page-main__features__items__3__subtitle
          様々な支払いに対応
        .top-page-main__features__items__3__detail
          お支払いは、クレジットカードだけでなく、ポイントや売上金など多彩な方法があります。
  .top-page-main__pickup-catgory
    .top-page-main__pickup-catgory__head
      ピックアップカテゴリー
    .top-page-main__pickup-catgory__box
      .top-page-main__pickup-catgory__box__title
        新規投稿商品
      .top-page-main__pickup-catgory__box__lists
        -@products.each do |product|
          .top-page-main__pickup-catgory__box__lists__img
            =link_to product_path(product), class: "top-page-main__pickup-catgory__box__lists__img" do
              .top-page-main__pickup-catgory__box__lists__img-inner
                = image_tag product.product_images[0].image.url
              .top-page-main__pickup-catgory__box__lists__img__body
                = product.name
                %br
                = "#{product.price}円"
                %br
                (税込)

  .top-page-main__pickup-brand
    .top-page-main__pickup-brand__head
      ピックアップブランド
    .top-page-main__pickup-brand__box
      .top-page-main__pickup-brand__box__title
        シャネル
      .top-page-main__pickup-brand__box__lists
        -@brand_1.each do |product|
          .top-page-main__pickup-brand__box__lists__img
            =link_to product_path(product), class: "top-page-main__pickup-catgory__box__lists__img" do
              .top-page-main__pickup-brand__box__lists__img-inner
                = image_tag product.product_images[0].image.url
              .top-page-main__pickup-brand__box__lists__img__body
                = product.name
                %br
                = "#{product.price}円"
                %br
                (税込)
